Mobis Brake Plant in Slovakia to Add 320 Jobs, Hospodarske Says

-- B y   R a d o s l a v   T o m e k
-- 
2011-04-26T07:20:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/mobis-brake-plant-in-slovakia-to-add-320-jobs-hospodarske-says.html
Hyundai Mobis (012330)  Co. will spend 18
million euros ($26 million) to build another factory in
 Slovakia , Hospodarske Noviny  reported .  The South Korean maker of automotive parts for Hyundai
Motor Co. and Kia Motors Corp. is to create 320 jobs at the
plant in Zilina, which will make brakes, the newspaper said,
citing project manager Slavomir Zbin.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Radoslav Tomek in Bratislava at 
 rtomek@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net . 